description:
Can we predict when Christ will return? Should we even be trying to set times for Christs return? Many theologians have speculated that the Cosmic Week concept - the biblical belief that God created the heavens and the Earth in six days and rested on the Seventh-day - if taken prophetically, can show us when the world will end, and when Christ will come.  Do they lead to the end of the world and the coming of Christ? What is the truth about this confusing timeframe? 
Dive into this exciting topic that spans 6000 years of sin, leading to a millennium with Christ. This presentation provides intriguing insights, emphasizing the importance of Bible study and prayer for understanding
